      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. It has been well-maintained, the engine runs smoothly, and the interior shows standard wear for its age. All major systems are functional and there are no significant mechanical issues.",
