      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade example that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, boasting a flawless exterior finish and a meticulously preserved interior that retains its original luster. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure peak performance and absolute perfection. For the discerning buyer who demands the pinnacle of automotive care, this specimen offers an unrivaled driving experience. Truly a rare find in such impeccable, turn-key state.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! It breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014it\u2019s practically showroom fresh and runs like an absolute dream. You won\u2019t find a single thing to worry about here; she\u2019s been kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and polished more often than my own shoes! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, come take a look. I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love the moment you hear the engine purr!",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a turn-key performance icon, optimized for the discerning enthusiast. The forced induction system has been pressure-tested for zero boost leak, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency across the map. We've implemented a custom stage-two map that optimizes ignition timing and AFRs for a visceral power delivery. The chassis rigidity is unparalleled, benefiting from a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and poly-bushing throughout. This unit has been garaged in a climate-controlled environment, preserving the integrity of every seal and gasket. It represents the pinnacle of its platform, delivering a raw, mechanical connection that modern drive-by-wire systems simply cannot replicate. Truly a museum-grade example for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Showroom quality. Zero flaws. Still smells new. First to see will buy. No games.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine gliding through the hills as the sun dips below the horizon, the engine of this Midnight Sapphire masterpiece humming a low, melodic tune that speaks of a thousand untold stories. This isn't just a vehicle; it's a preserved moment in history, a time capsule of elegance where the scent of hand-stitched leather still lingers like a fine cologne. Every curve of its polished silhouette reflects a commitment to craftsmanship that the modern world has forgotten. To sit behind the wheel is to command a legacy of power and grace, a silent promise of endless horizons. It awaits a curator who understands that true beauty isn't measured in miles, but in the heartbeat of the drive.",
      "price": 48750.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly impeccable condition. This specimen has been curated with the utmost care, presenting in a state indistinguishable from the day it left the showroom floor. Every surface, from the hand-polished exterior to the pristine, smoke-free cabin, reflects a standard of maintenance rarely seen on the pre-owned market. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically perfect, this is an investment-grade vehicle for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than the absolute best.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm finally ready to pass on my absolute pride and joy to a new home. This beauty has been my weekend darling, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single Sunday. It honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like an absolute dream\u2014so smooth and responsive, you'll fall in love the moment you hit the road. There might be a microscopic stone chip if you're looking with a literal magnifying glass, but she\u2019s as close to perfect as they come. I\u2019ve poured a lot of love into this car, and I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate her just as much. Swing by, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you around!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously sorted 2004 E46 M3, a purist\u2019s spec featuring the legendary S54 power plant with its high-revving individual throttle bodies and a crisp ZF 6-speed manual. The chassis is exceptionally tight; the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue, ensuring structural rigidity during aggressive cornering. Recent top-end work includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul with cryo-treated hubs and Beisan seals, effectively bulletproofing the variable valve timing. Suspension geometry is dialed in with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing surgical turn-in and zero cowl shake. This is a mechanically transparent, analog masterpiece maintained to a standard that exceeds the 'driver' category, presenting as a true turn-key investment.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_8",
